title: Leopard Gecko Warning Sign, Funny small Pet sign, Lizard warning sign
description: Display this little beauty to give warning to all those that may trespass while your Leopard Gecko is on guard duty. A perfectly versatile full color signs that is guaranteed to make a perfect gift or accessory for any garage, Man Cave, Wall Accent, child's room, and anything else you can think of. ************************ Product Outline ********************* Crafted from high quality aluminum, these full color signs are designed and thermally imprinted with eco-friendly inks, right here in Michigan! Our creative process uses extremely high temperatures to fuse the image to the surface, creating a look that is vibrant and scratch resistant! *Use the menu on the right to pick your style. New - a clean looking bright colored version of the sign. Distressed wood - has vintage look similar to distressed painted wood signs Aged Metal - resembles a vintage metal sign that is showing years with rust and dull color. Listing is for one, one sided aluminum sign that is 12" x 8" and .025" thick. Also comes with 2 holes pre drilled(centered on the shorter edges) ************************* Important Information ************** * Due to differences in computer screens the design color may appear slightly different than actual product. * If you would like a custom or personalized sign, or even just a specialized color please message us and we will be happy to help! These signs are designed to be displayed indoors. They will withstand the outdoors for some time will be fade overtime(around a 1 to 1 1/2 years).
